name: Janky Frog
description:
Janky Frog is a short, first person platformer. You are a small frog in a big world, making your way around and just trying to help.

Features:

  • Janky movement
  • Frog tongue
  • Janky frog tongue
  • Short
  • Been compared to spiderman
  • Been called "a bit of an unplayable mess"

Janky Frog is still in development and is in no way complete.
